<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.9.7">
<l>māṭṭī rāṉīr paṇinīr koḷḷa vemmaip paṇiyaṟiyā</l>
<l>viṭṭī ritaṉai vēṟē coṉṉō minta ḷūrīrē</l>
<l>kāṭṭī rāṉīr nunta maṭikkaḷ kāṭṭi lumakkinta</l>
<l>nāṭṭē vantu toṇṭa rāṉa nāṅka ḷuyyōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You are one who refuses to accept [us] in service;</l>
<l rend="indent">you abandoned us [even] while knowing of our devotion.</l>
<l>We said this is different [than expected], you of Intaḷūr.</l>
<l>You are one who does not reveal his feet; if you revealed [them],</l>
<l>Wouldn’t we, who are servants coming to this land for you, be saved?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
